Print the following pattern for the given N number of rows.
Pattern for N = 4

   1
  12
 123
1234

_____________________________________________________________________

n = int(input())
i = 1
while i<=n:
    space =1
    while space <= n-i:
        print(" ",end='')
        space = space+1
    j = 1
    while j<=i:
        print(j,end='')
        j = j+1
    print()
    i = i+1
